#| "targets three creatures in a row.  The Unit directly hit in the middle "
#| "suffers full damage, while the Units on both sides suffer 3\\,"
#| "\\svg{damage-red} less.  \\item A piece of armor, shield, or clothing: "
#| "The Dragon gains 3\\,\\svg{defense}, represented with spare Faction "
#| "cubes.  Remove them after they have absorbed damage.  \\item A trinket: "
#| "The Azure Dragon roars and summons an ice storm, causing all creatures to "
#| "freeze in fear.  This results in every Unit moving only 1 Field per "
