"\\svg{damage-red}.  \\item Consuming a Diamond Golem: Remove 4 \\svg{damage-"
"red}.  \\item[] \\textbf{Note:} The Crystal Dragon can only consume one "
"Golem per Turn.  \\end{itemize} \\item Golem Abilities: Gold and Diamond "
